{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-28","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor kombinacije poslednjeg i sloga.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da bi izgovorio/la <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iou</span>, počinjete postavljanjem jezika visoko i blizu tvrde nepme sa zvukom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>​.​</p>\n<p>Zatim, jednim kontinuiranim i glatkim pokretom, gurate jezik unazad i nadole do najotvorenije pozicije sa savijenim usnama za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, odmah praćen dodatnim povlačenjem nazad i savijanjem usana sa većom snagom za zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>.</p>\n<p>Celokupan tok mora biti neprekidan, formirajući jednu neprekidnu slogu.</p>\n<p>Ako je prvobitno, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iou</span> se često piše kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iu</span>. Zato vidiš slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">liu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">jiu</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiu</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">xiu</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">liu</span> u različitim tonomima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">liū</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">溜</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">liú</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">流</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">liǔ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">柳</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">liù</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">六</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-28"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":385.55,"finishTimestamp":405.93},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.97,"dialogue":{"text":"iou","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.34,"finishTime":4.28,"dialogue":{"text":"liu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.83,"finishTime":6.69,"dialogue":{"text":"jiu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.98,"finishTime":9.08,"dialogue":{"text":"qiu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.26,"finishTime":11.33,"dialogue":{"text":"xiu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.48,"finishTime":14.29,"dialogue":{"text":"liū","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":15.53,"finishTime":16.31,"dialogue":{"text":"liú","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":17.76,"finishTime":18.85,"dialogue":{"text":"liǔ","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.22,"finishT